*.rd files are containers for prose sections, that get 
injected into resource directory documents built by
util/rd/build-rd.xsl

The position of the injection in the result document 
is determined by using class attributes in the .rd
file. The following expressions are recognized by
build-rd.xsl:

div.intro
Contents injected to an informative introduction section,
under a h2 "Introduction".

div.normative-top
Contents injected to the start of the normative section,
under a h2 "Normative References".

div.normative-bottom
Contents injected to the end of the normative section

div.examples
Adds the content to the examples section, under a h2 "Examples"
